{"word":"G4021 - περίεργος - períergos - per-ee'-er-gos - Busybody","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περίεργος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>períergos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>per-ee'-er-gos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Busybody"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"மாயவித்தைக்காரரான, வீணலுவற் காரரான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"busy about trifles and neglectful of important matters, especially busy about other folks' affairs, a busybody"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2041 - ἔργον - érgon - er'-gon/2041\">G2041</a>; <i>working all around</i>, that is, <i>officious</i> (<i>meddlesome</i>, neuter plural <i>magic</i>): - busybody, curious arts."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}